{
  "name": "WF3 — Missed Appointment Recovery",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Workflow 3: Missed Appointment Recovery\n\n**Trigger:** Daily at 10:00 AM\n\n**Logic:**\n- Day +1: Sends empathetic recovery message\n- Day +3: Sends second nudge referencing the doctor\n- Day +7: Marks patient status as `missed` (stops messaging)\n\nPatients must have `follow_up_date < today` AND `status != completed` AND `status != inactive`.\n\n**Before activating:**\n1. Set credential on all Google Sheets nodes → Google Sheets account\n2. Set credential on HTTP Request nodes → Twilio Basic Auth",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 420
      },
      "id": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-000000000001",
      "name": "Sticky Note",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [240, 60]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "rule": {
          "interval": [
            {
              "field": "cronExpression",
              "expression": "0 10 * * *"
            }
          ]
        }
      },
      "id": "33333333-3333-3333-3333-000000000002",
      "name": "Daily 10AM Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.scheduleTrigger",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [240, 380]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "operation": "read",
        "documentId": {
